<div1 xml:lang="en" type="document">

<pb n="Scan20020"/>

<note>Department of State Received Sep 17 1883</note>

<note>No 49.</note>

<p>Consulate of the United States of America<lb/> 
at St Paul de Loanda<lb/>
S.W. Coast of Africa.</p>

<p>Ls de R. du Verge<lb/>
to State Dept.<lb/>
Washington D.C.</p>

<p>Subject</p>

<p>Congo River &amp;a &amp;a</p>

<p>Encloses</p>

<p>Statement of Affairs and abuses arising then.</p>

<pb n="Scan20021"/>

<p>United States Consulate<lb/>
St Paul de Loanda S.W.C. Africa<lb/>
July 7th 1883.</p>

<p>To<lb/>
Hon John Davis<lb/>
Asst. Secty. of State<lb/>
Washington D.C.</p>

<p>Sir</p>

<p>I have the honor respectfully to
enclose herewith memorandum of the <unclear extent="one word"/>
Affair, Slaves &amp;a &amp;a are conducted bought sold
&amp;a on the Congo and at the principal factories 
of the Left and right land</p>

<p>I have the honor to be<lb/>
Sir<lb/>
Your obt servt<lb/>
Ls de R. du Verge<lb/>
US Consul</p>

<p>"One Enclosure"</p>

</div1>

